{"type": "article", "id": 12107, "title": "“Abstract_”情绪也可以变衣服", "description": "", "date": "2015-07-15T11:03:45Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000039EDjyUs4Bu7z0SPpn.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦设计师 Kristine Boesen ，Julie Hells Eriksen 和 Bjorn Karman 联手推出了一个叫做 “Abstract_” 的跨学科项目，试图将个人情感通过图像的形式表达出来，并打印到衣服上去，设计出属于用户独一无二的衣物来。这个程序的原理是通过分析使用者敲击键盘的节奏以及捕捉用户的表情，同时分析纺织品面料，色彩，工艺等元素，通过复杂的算法，得到一个属于用户的独特的设计，并最终呈现在服装上。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135948lsEbOCnefuTMp8N0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44743276\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135949CU48cl1TB6IygXMF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.44743276\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135950bkWCiGJa1zs3V65c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726135950rhUEl1ebGFpL4f0x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261359515MG8YPo0LqRO6Eyd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}